{"id": "QmcWUQaRj7jVVB17h33yMGttgGkabgvWkh8tcKAaqf5idK", "title": "Response to Halving Bug", "body": "# Purpose:\n\nWe managed to partially fix the halving bug, but there was still an issue.\n\nOur transaction was supposed to properly map out all the halving blocks again, but instead it pushed back the first halving by 14 days and set the others to be 1 block apart.\n\nThis just means we'll need to manually update the halvings each time.\n\nIt also means there are two additional weeks at 4096x bonus multiplier.\n\nWe have a few options:\n\n1. Set a timelock transaction to lower the base block reward from 1000 -> 500 which will do the same as if the halving was taking place.\n\n2. Leave the extra bonus period and have a higher supply.\n\n3. Leave the current bonus period, but lower rewards in the future weeks when we resolving the halving blocks.", "choices": ["1", "2", "3"], "start": 1608138000, "end": 1608310800, "snapshot": "11466211", "state": "closed", "author": "0x3bC3c8aF8CFe3dFC9bA1A57c7C3b653e3f6d6951", "space": {"id": "baovotes.eth", "name": "baovotes.eth"}, "votes": 16, "votes_data": [{"id": "QmPvtxqbCTvrP4FAhQF1zGJmYg6c8YPq52QFPm3Q2aQ9y8", "voter": "0x76A8d26B61495A4a8f60E08bE83912194a820A5C", "created": 1608302019, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "baovotes.eth"}}, {"id": "QmWAbiBbEtF4mmvTVJKSHDr58Bk7vZkLPPmfZ5SuLFrZqy", "voter": "0x1b43BCaf30a19D3C619E8AFf02Fe134f66AAdc8B", "created": 1608258117, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "baovotes.eth"}}, {"id": "Qma5sknaqYeoEm6jfikD3XCFPgxz6uPRuEqBwT8cJYMYF1", "voter": "0xD68AaaC54a20D88151f5D12289fE1c79f05DFD9B", "created": 1608250103, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "baovotes.eth"}}, {"id": "QmVyvHjoDZNfyNkpZ19ewqcXSUqoSmBrHrA4jrCdYP4pKu", "voter": "0x495541aE43B68C362193aA2eF893006Ccc202d9A", "created": 1608230546, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "baovotes.eth"}}, {"id": "QmXUZxpM7hXas9zbbzUiDiG4Kn5WoXvfEALPqKe9JRLHXG", "voter": "0x553056Aa3D266Df15b7E1a291358CfEE56a1Be75", "created": 1608224754, "choice": 1, "space": {"i